    </ol>
</div>
<p style='margin-right:0cm;margin-left:35.4pt;font-size:16px;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;margin:0cm;text-align:justify;'><strong><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;'>&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<div style='margin:0cm;font-size:16px;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;'>
    <ol style="margin-bottom:0cm;list-style-type: undefined;margin-left:47.15px;">
        <li style='margin:0cm;font-size:16px;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;'><strong><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;font-size:12.0pt;'>FIDEICOMISO:&nbsp;</span></strong><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;font-size:12.0pt;'>Es el fideicomiso de inversi&oacute;n n&uacute;mero 256340<strong>&nbsp;</strong>celebrado con el Banco &ldquo;HSBC M&Eacute;XICO&rdquo;, SOCIEDAD AN&Oacute;NIMA, INSTITUCI&Oacute;N DE BANCA M&Uacute;LTIPLE, GRUPO FINANCIERO HSBC, al que estar&aacute; sujeto el &ldquo;FRACCIONAMIENTO&rdquo;, destinado a su mantenimiento.</span></li>
    </ol>
